name: Andrew Benson
tweet: The film puts a strong emphasis on Mosley’s important work in road safety and his fight to impose crash-test standards on car manufacturers, which has saved many thousands of lives, as well as his privacy campaign against the British tabloid newspapers 8/

name: Andrew Benson
tweet: And there is tragedy when it comes to the death from a drug overdose of his son Alexander, and Mosley has to confront the possibility that the newspaper story and his own actions contributed to his loss  7/

name: Andrew Benson
tweet: If you knew Mosley, this is him. All the many facets of his character are on display, positive and negative - his intelligence, his determination, his love of confrontation, his total lack of shame or embarrassment after being exposed in an orgy with prostitutes by a newspaper 6/

name: Andrew Benson
tweet: It confronts many of the key aspects his life head on - including his family history, and the effect it had on him both as a child and in his ambitions and work for many decades thereafter 5/

name: Andrew Benson
tweet: Based on extensive interviews with Mosley, Ecclestone, actor Hugh Grant and many other major figures through his working life, it paints a full picture of this complex and driven man 4/
